OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FCouncillors in Birmingham are set to
OL,8,Fconsider an unusual rotating
OL,9,Fleadership deal that could see a
OL,10,FLiberal Democrat lead the city council
OL,11,Ffor the first time.
OL,13,FUnder the proposal being brought
OL,14,Fforward on Friday, a coalition of the
OL,15,FGreens and Liberal Democrats would
OL,16,Fjointly run the authority, despite not
OL,17,Fhaving the 51 seats needed for a
OL,18,Fmajority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
