OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780391237
OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrat group leader,
OL,8,FRoger Harmer, would be put forward as
OL,9,Fthe first council leader under the
OL,10,Farrangement.
OL,12,FThe plan would then see leadership
OL,13,Frotate at a later date to Green group
OL,14,Fleader Julien Pritchard, although the
OL,15,Ftiming of that switch has not yet been
OL,16,Fagreed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780391237
OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FWith backing from the Better
OL,8,FBirmingham Independents, the proposed
OL,9,Fcoalition would command around 40
OL,10,Fcouncillors - short of a majority, but
OL,11,Fenough, its backers argue, to form a
OL,12,Fworkable administration in a
OL,13,Ffragmented chamber.
OL,15,FIt would mark a first for Birmingham
OL,16,FCity Council - a formally shared
OL,17,Fleadership model between parties,
OL,18,Funder what coalition figures are
OL,19,Fdescribing as a "joint leadership"
OL,20,Farrangement.
OL,26,@{D@QOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780391237
OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FBehind the scenes, talks are still
OL,8,Fongoing to finalise the agreement
OL,9,Fahead of Friday's full council
OL,10,Fmeeting, which begins at 6pm.
OL,12,FSenior figures within the proposed
OL,13,Fcoalition believe Labour councillors
OL,14,Fare unlikely to oppose the plan.
OL,16,FBut its success would also depend on
OL,17,FConservative, Reform UK and other
OL,18,Findependent councillors either backing
OL,19,For abstaining.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780391237
OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FIf an alternative leadership proposal
OL,8,Fis tabled, it would also be voted on -
OL,9,Fthough both Labour and Reform UK have
OL,10,Falready indicated they are not seeking
OL,11,Fto take control of the council.
OL,13,FIf elected, Roger Harmer would set out
OL,14,Fcabinet positions and scrutiny
OL,15,Fcommittee chairs at the same meeting
OL,16,Fon Friday, with those details still
OL,17,Fbeing finalised.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
