CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780391237
OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FCoalition figures acknowledge the
OL,8,Fmaths is tight - Greens (19), Liberal
OL,9,FDemocrats (12) and Better Birmingham
OL,10,Findependents still fall short of a
OL,11,Fmajority.
OL,13,FBut they argue there is already broad
OL,14,Fagreement on policy direction.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780391237
OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FOne senior figure involved in talks
OL,8,Fsaid there is "quite a lot of
OL,9,Fconsensus" on the city's priorities,
OL,10,Fadding the group would "listen very
OL,11,Fcarefully to other parties" and "play
OL,12,Fthe game fairly" as part of what they
OL,13,Fdescribe as a new way of operating.
OL,15,FDespite that, the central challenge
OL,16,Fremains political rather than policy-
OL,17,Fbased: whether enough councillors
OL,18,Foutside the coalition choose to back -
OL,19,For at least not block - the proposal.
OL,26,@pD@OOUqD@JO]rD@XOUsD@[O]sD@aOUtD@PO]
