OL,3,CGreens and Lib Dems to propose
OL,4,Crotating leadership of Birmingham City
OL,5,CCouncil
OL,7,FIf agreed, it would set up an unusual
OL,8,Farrangement in which leadership is
OL,9,Feffectively shared over time, even
OL,10,Fthough only one person can formally
OL,11,Fhold the office at any given moment.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/8
